    "file_type": "rst",
    "content": "﻿.. _dp-Zoom_Bar_Information:\n\nCrDeviceProperty_Zoom_Bar_Information\n=====================================\n\nGet the zoom bar information.\n\n.. list-table::\n    :widths: auto\n\n    *   - CrDataType\n        - CrDataType_UInt32\n\n.. raw:: html\n\n    <table class=\"docutils align-default\">\n        <tr>\n            <th colspan=\"2\">Value</th>\n            <th>Explanation</th>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td colspan=\"2\">31-24bit</td>\n            <td>Total box number</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td></td>\n            <td>0</td>\n            <td>min</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td></td>\n            <td>0xFF</td>\n            <td>max</td>\n        </tr> \n        <tr>\n            <td></td>\n            <td>1</td>\n            <td>step</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td colspan=\"2\">23-16bit</td>\n            <td>Current box number</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td></td>\n            <td>0</td>\n            <td>min</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td></td>\n            <td>0xFF</td>\n            <td>max</td>\n        </tr> \n        <tr>\n            <td></td>\n            <td>1</td>\n            <td>step</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td colspan=\"2\">15-0bit</td>\n            <td>Zoom position in Current Box</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td></td>\n            <td>0x00</td>\n            <td>min</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td></td>\n            <td>0x64</td>\n            <td>max</td>\n        </tr> \n        <tr>\n            <td></td>\n            <td>0x01</td>\n            <td>step</td>\n        </tr>\n\n    </table>\n\n.. image:: /_images/dp_Zoom_Bar_Information_fig.png\n    :width: 50%\n\nCurrentValue contains the following values:\n\nValue 1 (31-24): Total box number\n\nValue 2 (23-16): Current box number\n\nValue 3 (15-0): Zoom position in current box",
